@leftside: web.0net.io is staging for our new Zeronet web client. We haven't been working on it for a few months as focus shifted back to our core crypto business (dealing with crypto winter). 

The MAIN purpose for this project is to support mobile users WITHOUT having to download and install a client. Hopefully, it serves its purpose to help boost adoption.

The problem with 0net.io is that its ONLY a proxy (not a client), so users DO NOT contribute back to the network.
